        "meta_description": "Jay Leno got choked up as he spoke about his four-decade marriage to his wife, Mavis Leno, at the Feminist Majority Foundation’s 16th Annual Global Women’s Rights Awards Gala, saying that he 'couldn't be prouder of her' and he enjoys 'taking care of her.'",
